Package codes.arrays

package codes.arrays
A package which lets the users, to implement different functions of arrays to solve problems in other classes.
Author:
Trishit Maji
  • Class
    Description
    ArrayBreaker<T>
    Class ArrayBreaker, implements interface ConversionTable which is used to get the row, column etc.
    ArrayConvertor<T>
    Class ArrayConvertor, implements interface SingleDimension and MultiDimension which is used to convert the single dimensional arrays into multi dimension and the multidimensional arrays into single dimension.
    ConversionTable<T>
    Interface ConversionTable, is implemented in class ArrayBreaker which is used to break the parts of the arrays of double and triple dimension.
    MultiDimension<T>
    Interface MultiDimension, is implemented in class ArrayConvertor which is used to convert the single dimensional arrays into multi dimension.
    SingleDimension<T>
    Interface SingleDimension, is implemented in class ArrayConvertor which is used to convert the multidimensional arrays into single dimension.
